data.description: Fantastic and clean one and a half story home with tasteful updates that include kitchen cabinets, stainless steel appliances, LVP flooring, updated main level bathroom,  and white trim throughout. Two bedrooms and full bathroom are located on the main level. The kitchen has a generous dining room addition that leads out to the large deck. Just off of the main level living room is the stairway leading up to the spacious 9x32 loft area that can be used as a 3rd bedroom. The lower level offers a large family room with electric fireplace! This home is located just off of Brooklyn Blvd South of I94 making commutes a breeze!
